item.description: Hi! Welcome to my own blog! This blog is meant for showing off my projects that I had been doing in the past 8 years I know how to code. I like to experiment a lot and make a lot of different prototypes - just in python - my go to prototyping language - I counted ~ 57 projects.
item.content:
Hi! Welcome to my own blog!

This blog is meant for showing off my projects that I had been doing in the past 8 years I know how to code. I like to experiment a lot and make a lot of different prototypes - just in python - my go to prototyping language - I counted ~ 57 projects.
